snippet.title: The Fabled | Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The Fabled is an upcoming Free To Play RPG made in Unreal Engine 5

The demo will first be accessible to early community supporters and those who have acquired a Mintpass. Don't miss out on this opportunity to play!
